    aa_i_Action

    public class QueenAction
extends aa_ActionDynamic
    Queens can be placed, removed, and moved. For movements, a vertical direction is assumed. Therefore, only the end point needs to be specified.
    Author:
    Ravi Mohan, R. Lunde
